    div(id="service" class="w-full flex flex-col items-center")
      div(class="lg:max-w-[1366px] w-full flex justify-center items-center lg:mx-auto mb-[50px] md:mb-[116px] lg:mb-[170px]")
        div(class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center leading-none")
          h3(class="title-underline text-font-gray text-lg md:text-[35px] mb-2.5 md:mb-[22px] lg:mb-[22px] md:pb-7") SERVICE ITEM
          span(class="text-subtitle-gray text-[15px] md:text-[28px] md:leading-none lg:mb-5") 服務項目
      div(class="lg:max-w-[1366px] w-full text-xs md:text-[23px] lg:mx-auto lg:px-4")
        div(class="space-y-7 md:space-y-[70px]")
          div(class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:space-x-[68px] border-b border-subtitle-gray px-4 pb-7 md:pb-[70px] last:pb-0")
            div(class="md:text-[32px] md:leading-none text-center text-border-blue mb-[15px] md:mb-[35px] lg:mb-0 whitespace-nowrap") 土地開發
            div(class="leading-[26px] md:leading-[63px]")
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 建設必須要有原料，而土地就是建設的原料
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 獲取土地資訊並判斷分析土地價值，透過談判、訂約取得土地。
          div(class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:space-x-[68px] border-b border-subtitle-gray px-4 pb-7 md:pb-[70px] last:pb-0")
            div(class="md:text-[32px] md:leading-none text-center text-border-blue mb-[15px] md:mb-[35px] lg:mb-0 whitespace-nowrap") 產品規劃
            div(class="leading-[26px] md:leading-[63px]")
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 藉由專業團隊的創意及巧思，將土地這個美好的原料轉而創造成舒適與安全的居住幸福空間。
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 階段工作：產品定位、市場區隔分析、產品規劃設計、建照申請。
          div(class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:space-x-[68px] border-b border-subtitle-gray px-4 pb-7 md:pb-[70px] last:pb-0")
            div(class="md:text-[32px] md:leading-none text-center text-border-blue mb-[15px] md:mb-[35px] lg:mb-0 whitespace-nowrap") 信託服務
            div(class="leading-[26px] md:leading-[63px]")
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full")
                |信託服務流程：
                ul(class="list-decimal pl-3.5")
                  li 地主、建商雙方簽訂「合建契約」完成
                  li 地主、建商、銀行…等三方簽訂「信託契約」完成。（信託契約保障內容:土地產權、資金管理與起造人信託。）
                  li 工程實施階段，銀行可確保已購戸巳繳價金可專款專用，提供金流服務。
                  li 興建完成後，信託銀行進行房地分配完成後，信託關係结束。
          div(class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:space-x-[68px] border-b border-subtitle-gray px-4 pb-7 md:pb-[70px] last:pb-0")
            div(class="md:text-[32px] md:leading-none text-center text-border-blue mb-[15px] md:mb-[35px] lg:mb-0 whitespace-nowrap") 房屋預售
            div(class="leading-[26px] md:leading-[63px]")
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 委由專業銷告團隊進行產品包裝、廣告宣傳、行銷企劃與銷售。
          div(class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:space-x-[68px] border-b border-subtitle-gray px-4 pb-7 md:pb-[70px] last:pb-0")
            div(class="md:text-[32px] md:leading-none text-center text-border-blue mb-[15px] md:mb-[35px] lg:mb-0 whitespace-nowrap") 營造管理
            div(class="leading-[26px] md:leading-[63px]")
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 施工品質是我們的不二堅持，施工監造皆由專案管理單位執行，讓顧客輕鬆享受完工後交屋的喜悦。
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 創新的工務整合，工程顧問在設計階段的參與，貢獻其施工經驗與技術，施工之遭遇問題回饋至設計上，故設計者對施工可行性有更正的判斷。
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 整合項目:營造承包、結構設計、建築設計、機電設計、燈光設計，景觀設計等工種以營造優質施工品質及制造最大成本效益。
          div(class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:space-x-[68px] border-b border-subtitle-gray px-4 pb-7 md:pb-[70px] last:pb-0")
            div(class="md:text-[32px] md:leading-none text-center text-border-blue mb-[15px] md:mb-[35px] lg:mb-0 whitespace-nowrap") 物業管理
            div(class="leading-[26px] md:leading-[63px]")
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 物業管理是物業的一種增值服務。協助建商與屋主在交屋期到管理委員會成立後各個階段，都能獲得專業妥善的物業服務。
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 物業管理除了提供建築物內勞務與服務外，更可延續建物生命與使用的基本需求外，更可藉由營運管理增加社區收入，以提升不動產與土地的價值。
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 物業服務項目包括:警衛保全、清潔勞務及設備設施類如電力、空調、升降機、給排水、安全系統等維護、修理、保養等三大類
          div(class="lg:flex lg:items-center lg:space-x-[68px] px-4 pb-7 md:pb-[70px] last:pb-0")
            div(class="md:text-[32px] md:leading-none text-center text-border-blue mb-[15px] md:mb-[35px] lg:mb-0 whitespace-nowrap") 售後服務
            div(class="leading-[26px] md:leading-[63px]")
              div(class="relative pl-3.5 md:pl-[30px] lg:pl-[33px] before:absolute before:top-[5px]  lg:before:top-[25px] before:left-0 before:w-[6px] md:before:w-[13px] before:h-[6px] md:before:h-[13px] before:bg-border-blue before:rounded-full") 完善交屋服務，包括專屬交屋手冊、售後服務卡、24小時內通報售後專責人員服務機制等，並進行客戶服務滿意度調查，讓住戶對建商的售後服務更信任。同時以同理心，在房屋成交後仍持續關心客戶居家狀況與社區管理維護，建立更優質的服務口碑與公司口牌。


